Deprecated. use de.systemagmbh.tools.io.CSysFile#getSubdirectories()

Returns an array of strings naming the directories in the directory denoted by this abstract pathname The behavior of this method is the same as that of the list() method, except only directory names are returned.

Parameters:
file - - A directory
Returns:
